1. MAKE SURE ALL FILES ARE COPIED INTO SAME DIRECTORY
2. CHANGE IP MANUALLY INTO THE CORRECT IP
3. PING TO 'KERBEROS' HOST NAME MUST WORKS FIRST
4. IF THIS IS FRESH COMPUTER SETUP, PLEASE CHOOSE "NEW INSTALLATION" AND "REBOOT"
5. AFTER THAT, YOU CAN CHOOSE AND INSTALL WHAT EVER NEEDED